,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T04:40:22.000Z","msg":"put life into a broader angle.<br />\ntry to bring love to others,<br />\nbe true to yourself.<br />\n<br />\nliving the process with be loved one is much rewarding then achieving  the goal alone.<br />\n<br />\nlook at all those dazzling celebrites and the love a simple man cam obtain."},{"pid":"5755986eacca906178200919c484a530b271bb71","tid":342893,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T04:41:47.000Z","msg":"存在先於本質"},{"pid":"6ee8ca4c807e3c23acc9aef5fcd04325be8c0faf","tid":342893,"uid":111354,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T04:52:44.000Z","msg":"開心share:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o5y8Uj_GMEk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Do5y8Uj_GMEk&d=WGN%2F9b88i5SI2hUCuOKJsGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=777ac42f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o5y8Uj_GMEk</a>"},{"pid":"bad73c830372e73561ed16bccdb98d6ccf2f2aa6","tid":342893,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T04:58:20.000Z","msg":"日日都諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28a48a51b28d78df41f236bf065e6e1d1c303f6c","tid":342893,"uid":51902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T04:59:27.000Z","msg":"我都覺得死亡好可怕  我唔在意生存有無意義  我只在意我死後唔可以再同朋友玩  周圍去睇個世界   一諗起終有一日會停止呼吸就好驚   但次次夜晚驚一陣都會逼自己唔再去諗ed野  第2朝瞓醒剩底既只有無奈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da9ffddefd478d39ae21b097d08b26f7b4e10b04","tid":342893,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T05:03:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"06c3b2fd1c4a2b4a02bf9a1fa234369116b61af7","tid":342893,"uid":66158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T05:05:22.000Z","msg":"上面巴打講個啲感覺 思考我全部都試過 <br />\n依家間唔時都會有<br />\n第一次係十幾歲無啦啦瞓落張床發呆 <br />\n無啦啦突然有一下好似悟頓咗 <br />\n個腦好似光速思考死亡嘅恐怖 同人生意義<br />\n個陣咁細個就諗到呢啲覺得好驚 即刻搵其他野做<br />\n但係之後就當自己一個好靜個陣又會諗呢啲野<br />\n<br />\n再大啲 諗諗下覺得 自己生命有限 唔想就咁過咗一生<br />\n咩都無做過 諗諗下無啦啦諗到自己終極夢想係可以做到一個可以正面影響過世界 留底自己大名係後世<br />\n比如發明過一啲科技可以影響依家或者將來嘅世界<br />\n好似Steve job , Elon musk咁<br />\n我知係好難 但唔咁難點叫夢想<br />\n<br />\n再大過啲經歷多咗 睇睇下啲電影個陣會無啦啦諗人生意義同哲學<br />\n諗諗下已經唔係好驚死亡<br />\n因為我哋只係三次元入面嘅一條蟲仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"254edc78620e902c42ac18c0e8541d9a80ed501a","tid":342893,"uid":92921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T05:13:09.000Z","msg":"經常"},{"pid":"5ef7ae53f50faf347575f0527d6a668fddf2cff8","tid":342893,"uid":92921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T05:21:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得死亡之後唔會有地獄天堂既野<br />\n只係好似你訓著教咁, 大家訓緊教個時係無意識, 只係訓前同醒後係有&ldquo;做緊人&rdquo;既感覺<br />\n而死亡係一樣, 當重新有意識個一刻就係成為bb重新出世個時</blockquote><br />\n可能&quot;做緊人&quot;先係發緊夢，而死亡先係訓醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3a984d14f791f32a0efbc2c06d9a45cc1c46adb","tid":342893,"uid":25267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T05:29:48.000Z","msg":"精靈寶鑽入邊講<br />\n死亡係依露維嘉給人類的禮物<br />\n我覺得講得幾好"},{"pid":"94dfc43424865f15a6ff517a245484f9bd6f4d88","tid":342893,"uid":25267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T05:31:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>精靈寶鑽入邊講<br />\n死亡係依露維塔給人類的禮物<br />\n我覺得講得幾好</blockquote>"},{"pid":"32330d60d170e554fdfd98ad7594268caf231fdc","tid":342893,"uid":11601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T05:34:29.000Z","msg":"經常都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2ee92eb21b79ba0bf3bbd9f8272f1f85632d21c","tid":342893,"uid":113657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T05:46:40.000Z","msg":"我都經常諗存在意義  有時諗下呢個宇宙點會咁有規則<br />\n動物點解設計到咁適合地球生存又平衡  有時又轉個角度睇  宇宙我覺得係一整個生命  乜都諗下  但身邊得一個朋友鐘意諗呢d  女仔更加少人諗哲學"},{"pid":"09b090a514629fe434132adf38e10e2e06510fc7","tid":342893,"uid":128869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T06:25:53.000Z","msg":"得閒睇兩本哲學 去體會下喜歡思考既人點思考呢個世界 <br />\n世界暫停未有發現到客觀真理 咁作為一個主觀個體唯一可以做既就係探求真理 <br />\n<br />\n或者人生係一場虛無 但如果曾經試過思考呢個世界 當中既滋味令你此生有意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60f1a88102584789295a95295a7f2294999dc503","tid":342893,"uid":128869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T06:32:45.000Z","msg":"個人認為人生既意義就係死亡<br />\n<br />\n因為人生既目的就係係有限既肉體同時間中 嘗試得到最多既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以懼怕死亡係不必要 珍惜自己重視既每一刻先係必要<br />\n<br />\n如果 人出世就係由無變有 既然我本來係「無」（nothing) 咁就算我有什麼 我都已經比「無 」有得更多野 <br />\n就算天命要我歸於「無 」如果我以整體黎睇 我無失去任何野 我無成本 只有收益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"120fab4f306f50614296ac16700bfbe60c105d53","tid":342893,"uid":501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T07:26:01.000Z","msg":"會呀<br />\n細個成日臨訓諗<br />\n諗諗下諗到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成日要勞煩阿媽黎安慰返我先訓到覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5241c3925a64989d35ab4c664f606374af55ad07","tid":342893,"uid":68284,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T07:44:04.000Z","msg":"中三已經會諗讀書有咩意義，再諗做人既意義係咩，發覺人生好虛無，跟住就想自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}